365
00:29:34,140 --> 00:29:35,859
[SPEAKER_00] znači jedan zajednički sastanak

366
00:29:35,859 --> 00:29:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] i onda je ono što zapravo slijedi,

367
00:29:38,119 --> 00:29:39,859
[SPEAKER_00] znači svako društvo koje se za to uči,

368
00:29:39,859 --> 00:29:42,819
[SPEAKER_00] samo potpisati policu,

369
00:29:42,819 --> 00:29:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] znači policu baš potpisati za Kroaciju osiguranje.

370
00:29:45,740 --> 00:29:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, te police će biti usklopljene

371
00:29:49,140 --> 00:29:50,759
[SPEAKER_00] sa neodređenim trajenjem,

372
00:29:50,759 --> 00:29:52,819
[SPEAKER_00] a moći će se raskinuti istakom

373
00:29:52,819 --> 00:29:54,660
[SPEAKER_00] svake osigurateljne godine.

374
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je proizvod koji smo sada uspjeli

375
00:29:58,680 --> 00:30:01,700
[SPEAKER_00] dobiti kao prvi, kao specijalan za tu drugu

376
00:30:01,700 --> 00:30:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] i zaista prvi na našem tržištu,

377
00:30:03,599 --> 00:30:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] a ono što nam je u cilju dalje

378
00:30:05,960 --> 00:30:08,680
[SPEAKER_00] raditi i sa drugim osigurateljima

379
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:10,859
[SPEAKER_00] da dobijemo one stvari koje sam reka

380
00:30:10,859 --> 00:30:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] da su nam još nedostajale ovdje

381
00:30:13,039 --> 00:30:14,779
[SPEAKER_00] i koje nam Kroacije u ovom momentu

382
00:30:14,779 --> 00:30:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] nije mogla dati,

383
00:30:15,579 --> 00:30:16,799
[SPEAKER_00] bilo zbog svojih problema

384
00:30:16,799 --> 00:30:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] s informatikama ili zbog svojih strahova,

385
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:20,740
[SPEAKER_00] ali koje vjerujem

386
00:30:20,740 --> 00:30:22,279
[SPEAKER_00] da će mako ne prije,

387
00:30:22,279 --> 00:30:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] a onda barim za godinu dana,

388
00:30:24,119 --> 00:30:25,680
[SPEAKER_00] moći poboljšati.

389
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:27,859
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bismo to mogli napraviti,

390
00:30:27,859 --> 00:30:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] u interesu nam je da se što više osoba osigura

391
00:30:31,420 --> 00:30:34,259
[SPEAKER_00] i da pokažemo da za ovu postoji interes

392
00:30:34,259 --> 00:30:36,660
[SPEAKER_00] i da ovo nije problematičan proizvod,

393
00:30:36,660 --> 00:30:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] da ovdje neće biti nekakvih iskoristavanja

394
00:30:39,900 --> 00:30:40,700
[SPEAKER_00] ili prijevara,

395
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:44,299
[SPEAKER_00] nego će biti zaista koristeno kao osiguranje,

396
00:30:44,799 --> 00:30:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] a ja vjerujem da su članice udruge

397
00:30:46,819 --> 00:30:48,640
[SPEAKER_00] podruzećne s povjerenjem

398
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] upravo prave,

399
00:30:50,119 --> 00:30:52,420
[SPEAKER_00] pravi klijenti za tako nešto.

400
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo zbog onoga što ta udruga promovira,

401
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:59,200
[SPEAKER_00] a to je zaista povjerenje

402
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] i jedno poštenje u poslovanju.

403
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, toliko od mene,

404
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:04,640
[SPEAKER_00] hvala i svoje nam na pitanja,

405
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:05,660
[SPEAKER_00] dalje pitanja.

406
00:31:05,660 --> 00:31:07,460
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala ti, draga Ksenija,

407
00:31:07,460 --> 00:31:08,980
[SPEAKER_02] lijepo je čuti da je netko

408
00:31:08,980 --> 00:31:11,240
[SPEAKER_02] na strani nas malih poduzetnika

409
00:31:11,240 --> 00:31:12,380
[SPEAKER_02] i ono kao što sam rekla

410
00:31:12,380 --> 00:31:13,420
[SPEAKER_02] u onom najavnom videu,

411
00:31:13,519 --> 00:31:15,779
[SPEAKER_02] mislim ti si broker koji nam omogućava

412
00:31:15,779 --> 00:31:17,079
[SPEAKER_02] da ne budemo broke,

413
00:31:17,079 --> 00:31:20,180
[SPEAKER_02] što se kaže u najtežim trenucima u životu

414
00:31:20,180 --> 00:31:21,119
[SPEAKER_02] kad smo bolesne

415
00:31:21,119 --> 00:31:23,500
[SPEAKER_02] i jadne same sebi moramo priznati

416
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:24,799
[SPEAKER_02] da ne možemo dalje,

417
00:31:24,799 --> 00:31:27,420
[SPEAKER_02] iako je to nama ženama često vrlo teško.

418
00:31:27,420 --> 00:31:29,559
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, otvorila bi sad

419
00:31:29,559 --> 00:31:32,019
[SPEAKER_02] mogućnost postavljanja pitanja

420
00:31:32,019 --> 00:31:34,000
[SPEAKER_02] našim današnjim sudionicama.

421
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,500
[SPEAKER_02] Možete u chat,

422
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:37,680
[SPEAKER_02] možete se javiti i u živo

423
00:31:37,680 --> 00:31:38,940
[SPEAKER_02] ako imate koje pitanje,

424
00:31:38,940 --> 00:31:40,559
[SPEAKER_02] a evo, ja ću odmah prvo pitanje,

425
00:31:40,559 --> 00:31:41,400
[SPEAKER_02] odmah volim pitati.

426
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:45,279
[SPEAKER_02] Za preglede specijalističke,

427
00:31:45,279 --> 00:31:47,299
[SPEAKER_02] znači to su poliklinike

428
00:31:47,299 --> 00:31:50,480
[SPEAKER_02] s kojima Kroacija osiguranje

429
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:52,019
[SPEAKER_02] ima sklopljen ugovor,

430
00:31:52,019 --> 00:31:52,460
[SPEAKER_02] je li tako,

431
00:31:52,460 --> 00:31:54,200
[SPEAKER_02] policu osiguranja zdravstvenog?

432
00:31:54,559 --> 00:31:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, da, Kroacija osiguranje

433
00:31:56,619 --> 00:31:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] na široku mrežu poliklinika.

434
00:31:58,599 --> 00:32:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se sklopiti policu,

435
00:32:00,079 --> 00:32:02,180
[SPEAKER_00] dobit će se popis svi tih poliklinika,

436
00:32:02,180 --> 00:32:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] koje oni, znači ne samo njihovih vlastitih

437
00:32:04,619 --> 00:32:06,160
[SPEAKER_00] poliklinika, imaju i takve,

438
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:07,859
[SPEAKER_00] recimo u Zagrebu postoji jedna

439
00:32:07,859 --> 00:32:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj ja dosta često znam

440
00:32:09,319 --> 00:32:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] i otići nekakve usluge obaviti,

441
00:32:10,900 --> 00:32:13,400
[SPEAKER_00] ali oni osim toga imaju ugovora

442
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] sa jednom cijelom mrežom riječnika

443
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:17,299
[SPEAKER_00] ili i poliklinika

444
00:32:17,299 --> 00:32:19,839
[SPEAKER_00] u kojima se može ubaviti usluka.

445
00:32:19,839 --> 00:32:22,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, evo, mislim da je Kroacija

446
00:32:22,119 --> 00:32:23,660
[SPEAKER_00] po tome dobar izbor.

447
00:32:23,660 --> 00:32:27,359
[SPEAKER_00] Pokrivam je široko područje po Hrvatskoj.

448
00:32:27,359 --> 00:32:29,039
[SPEAKER_02] Imam još jedno pitanje.

449
00:32:29,039 --> 00:32:33,480
[SPEAKER_02] Hoće li polica pokrivati one dane

450
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:35,519
[SPEAKER_02] kad su, na primjer, djeca bolesna?

451
00:32:35,519 --> 00:32:38,180
[SPEAKER_02] Jel puno nas ima dosta djece,

452
00:32:38,180 --> 00:32:39,940
[SPEAKER_02] tri i više,

453
00:32:39,940 --> 00:32:41,640
[SPEAKER_02] tako da, evo, mene zanima

454
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:43,180
[SPEAKER_02] što se tad događa.

455
00:32:43,180 --> 00:32:44,819
[SPEAKER_02] Jer, na primjer, ako si zaposlena

456
00:32:44,819 --> 00:32:46,240
[SPEAKER_02] na nekoj firmi ili korporaciji,

457
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,900
[SPEAKER_02] onda uzmeš bolovanje

458
00:32:47,900 --> 00:32:49,119
[SPEAKER_02] jer ti djete bolesno.

459
00:32:49,119 --> 00:32:52,180
[SPEAKER_02] Što u trenucima takvim?

460
00:32:52,180 --> 00:32:54,240
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ako ste na bolovanju,

461
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] to polica pokriva.

462
00:32:55,599 --> 00:32:57,400
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ako ste vi osobno na bolovanju

463
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:58,779
[SPEAKER_00] zbog bilo kojeg razloga,

464
00:32:58,779 --> 00:33:00,140
[SPEAKER_00] to će polica pokriti.

465
00:33:00,140 --> 00:33:01,519
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, čak i ako smo na bolovanju

466
00:33:01,519 --> 00:33:01,980
[SPEAKER_02] zbog djete.

467
00:33:01,980 --> 00:33:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, tako je.

468
00:33:04,900 --> 00:33:05,779
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ono što nam je upravo

469
00:33:05,779 --> 00:33:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] nastao kao problem,

470
00:33:06,759 --> 00:33:08,339
[SPEAKER_00] znači što Kroacija ne može znać

471
00:33:08,339 --> 00:33:09,640
[SPEAKER_00] dok čega ste vi na bolovanju.

472
00:33:09,640 --> 00:33:11,319
[SPEAKER_00] Tu nam je malo nastao problem,

473
00:33:11,420 --> 00:33:12,160
[SPEAKER_00] upravo jer smo željeli

